titocc.compiler.types

Class IntType

  • java.lang.Object
    • titocc.compiler.types.CType
      • titocc.compiler.types.IntType

  • public class IntType
extends CType
    Corresponds to C int type. Is an object, scalar, arithmetic and integer type, but not arithmetic. Equals only to IntType.
